WEBVTT

00:00:29.746 --> 00:00:33.787
che potessi vincere 
32 computer contemporaneamente.

00:00:34.496 --> 00:00:37.037
Per me, quella fu l’età dell’oro.

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:39.162
(Risate)

00:00:39.204 --> 00:00:40.704
Le macchine erano deboli,

00:00:41.662 --> 00:00:42.996
e i miei capelli forti.

00:00:43.037 --> 00:00:45.246
(Risate)

00:00:46.704 --> 00:00:48.787
Solo 12 anni dopo,

00:00:48.787 --> 00:00:53.412
mi stavo giocando la vita
contro un solo computer

00:00:53.454 --> 00:00:54.621
in una partita

00:00:55.371 --> 00:00:57.412
chiamata dalla copertina di “Newsweek”

00:00:57.454 --> 00:00:59.204
“L’ultima Battaglia del Cervello.”

00:00:59.246 --> 00:01:00.454
Nessuna pressione.